---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';

const sidebar = [
	{
		title: 'Docs',
		links: [
			{ href: '/docs', label: 'Intro' }
		]
	},
	{
		title: 'PrismChart',
		collapsible: true,
		expanded: true,
		links: [
			{ href: '/docs/prismchart', label: 'Overview' },
			{ href: '/docs/prismchart/installation', label: 'Installation' },
			{ href: '/docs/prismchart/foundation', label: 'Foundation', active: true },
			{ href: '/docs/prismchart/chart-tools', label: 'Chart Tools' },
			{ href: '/docs/prismchart/development', label: 'Development' },
			{ href: '/docs/prismchart/credits', label: 'Credits' }
		]
	}
];

const toc = [
	{ href: '#video', label: 'Video' },
	{ href: '#price-scale', label: 'Price Scale' },
	{ href: '#time-scale', label: 'Time Scale' },
	{ href: '#zoom', label: 'Zoom' }
];
---

<DocsLayout title="Foundation - PrismChart - Docs" sidebar={sidebar} toc={toc} issuesUrl="https://github.com/ether-strannik/PrismChart/issues">
	<style>
		h1 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
			font-weight: 600;
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		}

		.tagline {
			color: #666;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			font-weight: 600;
			margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
			padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
			border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
		}

		h3 {
			font-size: 1rem;
			font-weight: 600;
			margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
		}

		p {
			color: #333;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}

		ul {
			padding-left: 1.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		li {
			padding: 0.3rem 0;
			color: #333;
		}

		.video-container {
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
			border-radius: 8px;
			overflow: hidden;
		}

		.video-container iframe {
			display: block;
			width: 100%;
			aspect-ratio: 16/9;
			border: none;
		}

		.note {
			color: #666;
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			padding: 1rem;
			background: #f5f5f5;
			border-radius: 4px;
			margin: 1.5rem 0;
		}
	</style>

	<h1>Foundation</h1>
	<p class="tagline">Custom coordinate system replacing MT5 defaults</p>

	<div class="video-container" id="video">
		<div id="yt-player"></div>
	</div>

	<script>
		const tag = document.createElement('script');
		tag.src = 'https://www.youtube.com/iframe_api';
		document.head.appendChild(tag);

		window.onYouTubeIframeAPIReady = function() {
			new YT.Player('yt-player', {
				videoId: '0BSx1YNXRtE',
				playerVars: { rel: 0, modestbranding: 1 },
				events: {
					onReady: function(e) { e.target.setPlaybackQuality('hd720'); }
				}
			});
		};
	</script>

	<p>MetaTrader 5's default chart display has limitations - it only shows broker time, which can be confusing when broker time 00:00 equals NY time 17:00. PrismChart replaces the coordinate system with fully customizable price and time scales.</p>

	<h2 id="price-scale">Price Scale</h2>
	<p>Canvas-based rendering replaces the default MT5 price axis with full customization:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Font family and size selection</li>
		<li>Text color and background color</li>
		<li>Rounded price levels at user-defined intervals</li>
		<li>Current price indicator displayed on scale</li>
	</ul>

	<h2 id="time-scale">Time Scale</h2>
	<p>TradingView-style timeline with timezone support:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Font family and size selection</li>
		<li>Text color and background color</li>
		<li>Separate colors for day, month, and year labels</li>
		<li>Adaptive format per timeframe (M1 through MN1)</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Timezone Modes</h3>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>New York (Auto DST)</strong> - automatically adjusts for daylight saving time</li>
		<li><strong>Manual UTC offset</strong> - set a fixed offset from UTC</li>
	</ul>

	<h2 id="zoom">Zoom</h2>
	<p>Fine-tuned zoom control with reasonable time segment display:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Custom zoom increments per timeframe</li>
		<li>Adaptive time segments at each zoom level</li>
		<li>Consistent experience across all timeframes</li>
	</ul>
</DocsLayout>
